iragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, 'lucida sans regular', 'lucida sans unicode', arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34,34,34); line-height: 1.8em;\">Writing: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Rim\" target=\"_blank\">Rim</a><br />\n\tRim means the outer edge. What is the rim referred to? Where is the rim found? How does it look? What is the importance?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They saw the rim... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) installing expensive rims on the car's wheels<br />\n\t2) a basketball hitting the rim of the hoop<br />\n\t3) wiping the rim before capping the bottle<br />\n\t4) putting salt on the rim of a cocktail glass<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIn this early morning, though, as soon as he walked into his office, the strong fragrance hit him in the face and completely caught him off guard. Shawn immediately looked towards the shelf where he placed the cologne bottle. It was sitting prettily on the shelf, just like it always did. While walking towards the shelf, he placed his bag on the sofa, so that he could carefully pick up the bottle with both hands, as the lid on the bottle was only balancing around the rim, not tightly secured.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意